videos.description: Brianna Turner puts finishes the aley-oop layup through a foul.
videos.headline: Turner gets and-1 layup off alley-oop

videos.description: Notre Dame takes momentum into halftime with a Lindsay Allen steal that leads to a buzzer beater layup.
videos.headline: Allen beats the buzzer with nifty fast break layup

videos.description: Back to back 3's by Kendall Cooper and Rebecca Greenwell have Duke staying close with Notre Dame in the ACC Championship game.
videos.headline: Duke staying close with 3-point shooting

videos.description: Notre Dame players celebrate after winning the ACC confrence championship tournament.
videos.headline: Notre Dame celebrates after winning ACC Championship

videos.description: After Notre Dame's ACC conference championship win bigger goals loom on the horizon for the Fighting Irish.
videos.headline: Postgame Breakdown on Notre Dame's expectations after winning ACC Conference Tournament

videos.description: No. 3 Notre Dame defeats No. 13 Duke 84-61 to win its fourth straight ACC crown.
videos.headline: Irish top Blue Devils for ACC title
